evidence.text: DONE AND ORDERED in Chambers in Miami, Florida, on this 7th day of August, 2025.
This TRO shall last fourteen (14) days from the date of this Order or until the Court enters an order as to Plaintiffs’ Motion for Preliminary Injunction.
